import { Container, TextField, Typography, Button, Box } from '@mui/material';

export default function AddProduct() {
  return (
    <Container>
      <Typography m={2} variant="h4" gutterBottom>
        Add Product Details
      </Typography>
      <Box m={2}>
        <TextField label="Product Name" variant="outlined" fullWidth />
      </Box>
      <Box
        component="form"
        sx={{
          '& > :not(style)': { m: 2, width: '25ch' }
        }}
        noValidate
        autoComplete="off"
      >
        <TextField label="Marked Price" variant="outlined" />
        <TextField label="Sale Price" variant="outlined" />
        <TextField label="Weight Info" variant="outlined" />
      </Box>
      <Box m={2}>
        <TextField label="Short Description" multiline rows={2} rowsMax={2} fullWidth />
      </Box>
      <Box m={2}>
        <TextField label="Long Description" multiline rows={6} rowsMax={4} fullWidth />
      </Box>
      <Typography m={2} variant="h5" gutterBottom>
        SEO Section
      </Typography>
      <Box m={2}>
        <TextField label="Meta Title" variant="outlined" fullWidth />
      </Box>
      <Box m={2}>
        <TextField label="Product Slug" variant="outlined" fullWidth />
      </Box>
      <Box m={2}>
        <TextField label="Meta Description" multiline rows={2} rowsMax={2} fullWidth />
      </Box>
      <Typography m={2} variant="h5" gutterBottom>
        Product Images
      </Typography>
      <Box m={2}>
        <Button>
          Upload
          <input type="file" hidden />
        </Button>
      </Box>
    </Container>
  );
}
